description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bank Staff Nurse Vacancies –&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently recruiting to our Trust Temporary Staffing Team - Bank on Us and we are seeking Registered nurses with a valid NMC registration that have been qualified for at least 6 months with acute hospital nursing experience. You must work well in a team and be reliable and enthusiastic with excellent communication skills, as well as adaptable and flexible to changing situations, working within Trust policies and the NMC Code of Conduct.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have bank shifts in the following areas at St Peters Hospital:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Emergency Department&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Medical Wards including Acute Medical Unit, Cardiology, Senior Adults Medical Services, Gastroenterology, Respiratory and Stroke&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Surgical Wards including the Surgical Assessment Unit and Surgical HDU&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Trauma and Orthopedics including Swan Ward and the Rowley Bristow Unit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Critical Care Unit with a combination of Intensive care beds and Medical HDU beds&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Across both Ashford and St Peters Sites we have bank shifts in the following areas:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ophthalmology&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Radiology&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Theatres&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Outpatients&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ashford Hospital facilities include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Day Surgery Unit&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Elective Orthopedic Units&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Trust also has clinical services in the following areas where we also have bank shifts available:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Woking Community Hospital – Bradley Unit (Stroke and Neuro Rehab)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;West Byfleet and Cranley Clinics&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Bank on Us Hourly Pay Rates from 1 April 2020 for Bank only Workers and Substantive Staffing working&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What we offer: Weekly pay! (every Thursday).  &lt;strong&gt;Regular or occasional shifts &lt;strong&gt;(full-time and/or part-time) &lt;/strong&gt;to suit you in line with business needs. &lt;/strong&gt;Book shifts on-line or call our friendly team to book, Paid induction time, Mandatory training and updates, NHS Pension scheme, Free uniform, Paid annual leave, on-site accommodation and support with Revalidation and CPD.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information please email Alice Lake, Temporary Staffing Team Leader alice.lake@nhs.net or Lisa Punter, Lead Nurse Workforce lisa.punter@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
